Package: blts-usb-tests
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, blts-usb-tests-config
Description: BLTS USB functional tests
 This package contains USB testing framework

Package: blts-usb-tests-config-example
Architecture: any
Provides: blts-usb-tests-config
Description: BLTS USB functional test config example
 This package contains example how to create config for BLTS USB tests. This
 config will not allow throughout testing for the hardware.

Package: blts-usb-tests-config-n900
Architecture: any
Provides: blts-usb-tests-config
Description: BLTS USB functional tests config for n900
 This package contains configuration files to do some USB testing for Nokia
 n900
